{"tid":2311562,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"今次真係忍唔住要屌時代冰室","createTime":"2020-12-04T07:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T23:58:42.000Z","uid":142600,"like":3,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8f0f590015d88523818d1f6f0e48b58c88773ac3","tid":2311562,"uid":142600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"我知你地下午茶餐好抵食而已又夠飽<br />\n所以我都成日嗌黎食<br />\n而你地<span class=\"gold\">西多士</span>係得一個既姐<br />\n唔似出面既茶記或者冰室咁有咩 <span class=\"gold\">芝心西多士/法蘭西多士</span><br />\n但我真心唔明<br />\n同你講左<span class=\"gold\">糖漿轉煉奶</span><br />\n你係有同我轉啊<br />\n但係點解<span class=\"red\">西多士入面既花生醬都同我轉埋做煉奶</span>????<br />\n<br />\n你地口號話咩<span class=\"gold\">無論時代點變 味道依然唔變</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">咁西多士入面個餡你都同我轉埋 咁味道有無變啊?</span><br />\n<br />\n黃店好係好...<br />\n但屌你老母黃藍是政見 廚房戇鳩就係戇鳩<br />\n港式傳統西多士都唔撚識整<br />\n個西多士既精髓其中之一就係個花生醬啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我理撚得你厚唔厚姐<br />\n<br />\n利申: 落order前講撚清楚叫廚房小心d係無事，如果乜都唔提好似我咁落order: 下午茶H4 糖漿轉煉奶，咁就會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfa68b45d82a2437367053aab36016ad50c84f4","tid":2311562,"uid":142600,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OqEZG0u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqEZG0u.png&h=dc5a5c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQAmVkL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQAmVkL.png&h=fa3c3c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖係呢到<br />\n我準備落去再換過第2份<br />\n真係屌出聲"},{"pid":"4351910da219fa4f222e70f505d8809a96e2e61b","tid":2311562,"uid":22362,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"打咁多嘢<br />\n不如出聲同人講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f94302a48fcf8a05a712dfe81d85d7930be7b1","tid":2311562,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"re